# Max

Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/IMPLEMENTATION.md` before implementing.

## Security boundaries

- LLM code lives only in `apps/api` (`ai` module).
- Playwright only in `apps/worker` and `libs/integrations/*`.
- Never put passwords, `storageState`, or `CREDENTIAL_KEK` in queue jobs, logs, or AI prompts.
- Worker fetches site credentials via HMAC internal grant API — not from Postgres.

## Code style

- TypeScript strict; match existing Nx/Nest/React patterns in the repo.
- Prefer small, focused changes aligned with the Phase 0 checklist in IMPLEMENTATION.md.
- Minimize scope — do not scaffold Phase 2+ (Rohlik, voice, mobile) unless asked.

## Docs

- Canonical specs live under `docs/specs/` (see IMPLEMENTATION map).
- Update `docs/IMPLEMENTATION.md` checkboxes when completing Phase 0 items.

## Path rules

When editing matching paths, also follow: `api.mdc`, `worker.mdc`, `spec-kit.mdc`, `web.mdc` under `.cursor/rules/`.
